The focus of <b>The Captain Class</b> is team sports. In particular, this thoughtfully-researched book explores the factors that create and perpetuate elite teams that exhibited multiple years of years of superior performance and championship success.

The rigid criteria that the author applied to identify elite teams narrowed the research focus to 16 teams across popular professional team sports including baseball, basketball, hockey, football, soccer, rugby and handball. The question that the author wanted to answer was "What to the most dominant team in history have in common?"



[book:The Captain Class: The Hidden Force that Creates the World's Greatest Teams|31869155] is one of the <a href="https://beantownweb.blogspot.com/2018/01/best-business-books-2017.html" target="_blank">Best Business Books of 2017</a>.

